Today, almost every business owns a website or has maintained an online presence. Websites have many purposes, ranging from sharing personal information to promoting a business. Although most people understand how to create a website, not everyone knows how to make money off of their site. Hence, if you’re looking to monetize your website, here are eight proven ways to do so: Affiliate marketing is a way for website owners to earn commission by promoting other people’s products on their site. When a visitor to your site clicks on one of the affiliate links and makes a purchase, you earn a commission. While this may sound simple, a lot goes into being a successful affiliate marketer.
